✓ Proverbs 24:13
Fetching Proverbs 24:14...
  "14": "  Know that wisdom is thus for your soul;\n  If you find it, then there will be a future,\n  And your hope will not be cut off.\n",
✓ Proverbs 24:14
Fetching Proverbs 24:15...
  "15": "  Do not lie in wait, O wicked man, against the dwelling of the righteous;\n  Do not destroy his resting place;\n",
✓ Proverbs 24:15
